linux-universal-app-installer (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Linux Universal App Installer
  * Support for .deb, .appimage, .tar.gz, .snap, and .flatpak packages
  * Modern PyQt5 GUI with drag-and-drop functionality
  * Professional desktop integration and post-installation setup

